Dear all,
 
registrations are now open for our upcoming workshop on "Landscape Genomics"

**When:** June 17-21, 2024
**Where:** EPFL, Lausanne, Switzerland

Join us to learn the fundamentals of this approach and hone your skills with cutting-edge methods. From obtaining environmental data using GIS to analysing genetic variation in R, this workshop covers it all. Discover statistical approaches for studying local adaptation and gain hands-on experience with tools like Sambada and LFMM. Cap it off with insights on result interpretation and experiment planning.

Ideal for those people eager to apply landscape genomics in evolutionary biology and conservation studies. 

